<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_14f6f79f-9fbd-4ea2-bd22-748b8ff999d8" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>S7C4</sptc><title id="_a4d86a32-2328-4eda-8e58-d2d97b0eb2da">Wall and ceiling linings</title><archive-num/><clause-variation href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/10642_1.2.0.xml" variation="NSW" variation-type="REPLACE">NSW REPLACE Clause</clause-variation><subclause id="_dddf601c-303c-4b8c-b9dd-cb8f60a558e6" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_38bb9576-14c3-4536-934c-665780538729">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A wall or ceiling lining system must comply with the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1324_2.0.0.xml#_98b60468-48ff-40b6-9c9a-57b1ad3cd803" id="_2e74c459-f686-43da-a307-0de4163a2802" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">group number</xref> specified in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/225_22.3.0.xml#_bb5cf7b0-1c26-403c-b5d9-b2510679b011" id="_d1566a9c-31d7-40d6-9cd6-d2ed470b427c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Table S7C4</xref> and for buildings not fitted with a sprinkler system (other than a FPAA101D or FPAA101H system) complying with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/167_0.9.0.xml#_481171d2-3952-490d-b64d-c3d3f5d7825a" id="_46d8169e-e7fb-443f-a9e5-0ee3211495dd" scope="local" type="specification">Specification 17</xref> have—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_69c38234-5f8e-4d39-a7de-c64f46aedcdb">a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1471_24.0.0.xml#_99aa38a2-f7eb-4ec9-8300-89665b9d393e" id="_1e934c37-e9a5-4e18-bf27-60654b8066c7" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">smoke growth rate index</xref> not more than 100; or</li><li id="_288317d7-2bd2-4e6c-b731-efc39baee1f6">an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1203_0.8.0.xml#_279816f7-f5fd-4c07-aab8-9c951ac56b00" id="_4230f806-60c1-4bb8-880e-5f21304b2ded" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">average specific extinction area</xref> less than 250 m<sup id="_91bab127-0949-4ae6-93b9-3c2b948b7b94">2</sup>/kg.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_f0a4ff5f-1332-409c-83d9-8d6c44f91203" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_16745b80-d184-409b-baa4-9b3cb1726f37">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>A <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1324_2.0.0.xml#_98b60468-48ff-40b6-9c9a-57b1ad3cd803" id="_a384d74f-2745-4556-88ab-58f8654ff92f" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">group number</xref> of a wall or ceiling lining and the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1471_24.0.0.xml#_99aa38a2-f7eb-4ec9-8300-89665b9d393e" id="_0c30580a-9cb6-4f1c-8c57-d3ee562bc971" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">smoke growth rate index</xref> or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1203_0.8.0.xml#_279816f7-f5fd-4c07-aab8-9c951ac56b00" id="_b7f7d5c0-76c2-478d-bf5a-9e7981ee4ab6" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">average specific extinction area</xref> must be determined by an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1175_0.13.0.xml#_52d35595-b475-460e-ac5e-5cd3e0a72e5f" id="_dc8c6b95-c69e-4988-ae22-f190e35ac5ba" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Accredited Testing Laboratory</xref> in accordance with AS 5637.1.</p></subclause><callout id="_ef813f4a-cb24-4e34-ab5a-b3794e54d795"><callout-type ncc-info-type="notes"/><p>Until adoption of the next edition of the NCC determination need not be undertaken by an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/1175_0.13.0.xml#_52d35595-b475-460e-ac5e-5cd3e0a72e5f" id="_b07ea907-e622-40a8-8675-dd86da3a1280" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Accredited Testing Laboratory</xref>.</p></callout><table-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/601d5817-38d4-46f4-a9ae-3e54027c73d5/225_22.3.0.xml" graph="None" id="_bb5cf7b0-1c26-403c-b5d9-b2510679b011"><num/><title id="_148fc399-4884-4e26-bd31-49cab69b2c8f"/></table-reference></clause>